sentences: Marcus studied at the Berklee College of Music in Boston, Massachusetts, between 1959 and 1961.
He gained experience playing in the bands of Stan Kenton, Herbie Mann and Larry Coryell from 1963 to 1973.
Marcus died in September 2005 in New Hope, Pennsylvania.
